relation: The follow-up to Flapbound! Naturally, I had to do this as well, solely for Lucas. He's such a happy fellow.
I saw an episode of Flapjack recently and couldn't help but wonder what the style would look like when applied to Earthbound characters

I had an old piece of art I used as a placeholder for the comic's title and finally decided to put a real title page up. The hardest part of this was deciding on how I wanted the text, so I made two versions: One for the comic and one for fanart.
